OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto violent disorder in Southampton in
OL,8,Fthe wake of the murder of Henry Nowak.
OL,10,FAppearing at Southampton Magistrates'
OL,11,FCourt, Daniel Frost, of Northam Road,
OL,12,FSouthampton, also pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fpossessing a dog lead with a metal
OL,14,Fcarabiner attached as an offensive
OL,15,Fweapon.
OL,17,FNola Bond, prosecuting, told the court
OL,18,Fthat Frost had thrown dustbins and a
OL,19,Fchair at police officers during the
OL,20,Fprotest in the Portswood area on June
OL,21,F2.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
