OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FShe added: "He had around his neck a
OL,7,Fdog lead with a carabiner and wrapped
OL,8,Fit around his knuckles and taunted
OL,9,Fpolice officers to come and take it
OL,10,Foff him."
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Anthony Callaway sent
OL,13,Fthe case to be sentenced at the city's
OL,14,Fcrown court after telling the court
OL,15,Fthe offences were too serious for the
OL,16,Fpowers of the magistrates' court.
OL,18,FHe remanded the defendant in custody
OL,19,Fand ordered a pre-sentence report for
OL,20,Fthe sentencing hearing to be held at
OL,21,Fthe crown court on July 16.
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@IO]
