OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FHe told the court: "Daniel Frost, a 44-
OL,7,Fyear-old man, comes to this court
OL,8,Ftoday and faces two separate matters
OL,9,Farising out of the same circumstances
OL,10,Fof violent disorder on 2 June and that
OL,11,Fis alleged to have arisen out of the
OL,12,Frecent demonstration in the Portswood
OL,13,Farea in relation to the death of a
OL,14,Fparticular subject, and that matter is
OL,15,Fthe subject of a crown court trial
OL,16,Frecently concluded.
OL,26,@nD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
