OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"The second offence is possession of
OL,7,Fan offensive weapon. Mr Frost has
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to both of these
OL,9,Fmatters and it seems to this court any
OL,10,Fsentence would be way out of the
OL,11,Fpowers of this court. The matter will
OL,12,Fgo to Southampton Crown Court."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
