PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe court was told that Frost had
OL,7,Fpreviously received 25 convictions for
OL,8,F55 offences, including an offence
OL,9,Fagainst the person in 2001, four
OL,10,Fpublic disorder offences between 2006
OL,11,Fand 2011, offences of failing to
OL,12,Fsurrender in 1999 and 2008, possession
OL,13,Fof a bladed article in 2009 and
OL,14,Fthreatening and abusive behaviour in
OL,15,F2010 and 2011.
OL,17,FOliver O'Connor, defending, said Frost
OL,18,Fhad two children but lived alone with
OL,19,Fhis dog.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
