PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FHe said: "He is at pains to tell the
OL,7,Fcourt of his shame of his involvement,
OL,8,Fone of the biggest regrets in his life.
OL,10,F"He is a vulnerable man, he is in
OL,11,Freceipt of PIP (personal independence
OL,12,Fpayment) as a result of a serious fall
OL,13,Fhe had leading to a hip replacement."
OL,15,FA second man, 50-year-old Matt Styler,
OL,16,Fof Orange Grove, Gosport, pleaded not
OL,17,Fguilty to assaulting a police officer.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
