PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe court heard that the veteran
OL,7,Fsoldier who served with the Parachute
OL,8,FRegiment was accused of kicking a
OL,9,Fpolice sergeant during the Portswood
OL,10,Fdisorder.
OL,12,FJudge Callaway said: "He has a wife
OL,13,Fand three children, has a previous
OL,14,Fmilitary career, suffers PTSD and
OL,15,Fother difficulties."
OL,17,FHe remanded Styler in custody until a
OL,18,Fpre-trial hearing to be held at
OL,19,FSouthampton Crown Court on June 26.
OL,26,@tD@VOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
