PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Hampshire Police Federation
OL,7,Fsays it took the decision to suspend
OL,8,Fits social media platforms following
OL,9,Fcredible threats against members.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: We had a sudden
OL,12,Fsurge in online and AI going through
OL,13,Fall platforms trying to find any
OL,14,Finformation they could about members,
OL,15,Fwith a view to threatening their
OL,16,Fsafety. This is unacceptable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"The safety and security of our
OL,7,Fmembers is our first priority.
OL,8,FMisidentified officers have been
OL,9,Fforced to leave their homes and had
OL,10,Fserious threats made against their
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,F"Eleven of our members, and a police
OL,14,Fdog, were injured in Southampton when
OL,15,Fbottles, bricks and wheelie bins where
OL,16,Fthrown at them, this was not protest.
OL,18,F"It is our duty as their Federation to
OL,19,Ftake all steps we can to keep our
OL,20,Fmembers safe ` whether they are
OL,21,Fthreatened in person or online.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780650345
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to violent disorder
OL,4,Cin Southampton after Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"The murder of Henry Nowak was a
OL,7,Ftragedy; his father Mark Nowak
OL,8,Fhighlighted after the sentencing of
OL,9,FHenry's killer that he did not want
OL,10,Fthe tragedy to inflame division or
OL,11,Fhostility.
OL,13,F"The IOPC are conducting an
OL,14,Findependent investigation into the
OL,15,Fcircumstances around Henry's death and
OL,16,Fwe echo their request for people to
OL,17,Fstop speculating on the case.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts remain with Henry's
OL,20,Ffamily and friends."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
